<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag 'profile_img.jpg', width: 200, alt: 'Profile image', class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                     role="progressbar"
                     aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                     aria-valuemax="100"
                     style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Learning to code has been an arduous task but well worth the time, sacrifice and growth. I hope to attain to
          much
          higher levels of understanding and ability as I continue to study and learn both for you and in my personal
          time.</p>
        <p>I am always learning and am always on the lookout for new technologies that catch my interest, truly excited
          about the opportunities that lay ahead of me in
          this field and I cannot wait to see what I will build next as web developer.</p>

        <%= render 'about_buttons' %>
        <%= render 'about_job_history' %>
        <%= render 'about_education' %>
        <%= render 'about_courses' %>
        <%= render 'about_experience' %>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>